So we've been calling
the Java Development Kit like a toolbox.

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:11.950
And what we mean by that is that the
Java Development Kit is software that

00:00:11.950 --> 00:00:16.420
allows your computer to read and
work with the Java programming language.

00:00:16.420 --> 00:00:19.590
This is sort of fundamentally
different than a software program,

00:00:19.590 --> 00:00:22.570
because it's more like an upgrade for
your computer.

00:00:22.570 --> 00:00:24.700
So as you're installing
the Java development kit,

00:00:24.700 --> 00:00:26.780
it might seem a little bit intimidating.

00:00:26.780 --> 00:00:29.760
But what I want to tell you right
now is do not worry about it.

00:00:29.760 --> 00:00:31.410
You're not going to break your computer.

00:00:31.410 --> 00:00:33.510
And we're going to go super
slowly through the steps and

00:00:33.510 --> 00:00:37.650
explain what you're doing very
explicitly as you do each step.

00:00:37.650 --> 00:00:40.070
That said,
sometimes students run into problems.

00:00:40.070 --> 00:00:43.670
So I want to give you some additional
tools to help you resolve those issues.

00:00:43.670 --> 00:00:47.260
