I've got three resources for you.

00:00:47.260 --> 00:00:50.550
First is the troubleshooting document,
linked in the instructor notes.

00:00:50.550 --> 00:00:54.340
Second, is the forums and chat, where
you can ask fellow students for help.

00:00:54.340 --> 00:00:57.600
